HEADWORD: Callidity
<hw>Cal*lid"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>calliditas</ets>.]</ety> <def>Acuteness of discernment;
cunningness; shrewdness.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Her eagly-eyed <qex>callidity</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>C.
Smart.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

